{"type":"text","timestamp":1783487138217,"sessionID":"ses_0bfeb66caffeOOxX7Bbz2N0h6m","part":{"id":"prt_f401dba46001jCulh8KMXLPRSI","messageID":"msg_f401d86f7001IZp4RruyQ0GwOx","sessionID":"ses_0bfeb66caffeOOxX7Bbz2N0h6m","type":"text","text":"## Goal\n- Execute the detached `deep-research` fan-out lineage `gpt55-fast-1` for the deep-loop unification merge-design stress test.\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Write only inside `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-1`.\n- Do not run `resolveArtifactRoot`; bind `artifact_dir` directly to `config.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir`.\n- `session_id`: `fanout-gpt55-fast-1-1783486518892-2qss01`.\n- Executor: `cli-opencode model=openai/gpt-5.5-fast`.\n- Loop: `research`, `config.stopPolicy: convergence`, `config.maxIterations: 10`.\n- Final response must be exactly: `FANOUT_LINEAGE_COMPLETE:gpt55-fast-1`.\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- Loaded `deep-research` skill references and workflow/state/convergence docs.\n- Initialized lineage artifact directory and state files.\n- Created:\n  - `deep-research-config.json`\n  - `deep-research-state.jsonl`\n  - `deep-research-strategy.md`\n  - `deep-research-findings-registry.json`\n  - `deep-research-dashboard.md`\n- Completed iteration 1:\n  - Focus: structural layout and ownership seams.\n  - `newInfoRatio`: `0.82`.\n  - Output files: `prompts/iteration-001.md`, `iterations/iteration-001.md`, `deltas/iter-001.jsonl`.\n- Completed iteration 2:\n  - Focus: bidirectional path-coupling inventory.\n  - `newInfoRatio`: `0.74`.\n  - Output files: `prompts/iteration-002.md`, `iterations/iteration-002.md`, `deltas/iter-002.jsonl`.\n- Updated state/strategy/registry/dashboard after iterations 1–2.\n\n### In Progress\n- Iteration 3 started.\n- Current focus: system-spec-kit tooling borrow / external contract boundaries.\n- Already read relevant sources for iteration 3:\n  - `deep-loop-runtime/lib/deep-loop/artifact-root.cjs`\n  - `system-spec-kit/shared/review-research-paths.cjs`\n  - `deep-loop-workflows/shared/synthesis/resource-map.cjs`\n  - `deep-loop-workflows/deep-research/scripts/reduce-state.cjs`\n  - `commands/deep/assets/deep_research_auto.yaml` sections around artifact root and spec validation.\n\n### Blocked\n- (none)\n\n## Key Decisions\n- Preserve `deep-loop-workflows` as public hub/mode packets and `deep-loop-runtime` as internal backend under merged `system-deep-loop`; do not flatten ownership.\n- Path rewrites must be atomic across command YAML, compiled command contracts, doctor routes/assets, agents, advisor code/tests/metadata, system-spec-kit config, and runtime docs.\n- Skip `spec.md` pre-init/write-back because user constrained writes to the lineage artifact directory only.\n\n## Next Steps\n- Finish iteration 3 outputs: `prompts/iteration-003.md`, `iterations/iteration-003.md`, `deltas/iter-003.jsonl`.\n- Append iteration 3 record to `deep-research-state.jsonl`.\n- Update `deep-research-strategy.md`, `deep-research-findings-registry.json`, and `deep-research-dashboard.md`.\n- Continue iterations until legal convergence or iteration 10.\n- Run phase_synthesis and write final synthesis artifacts inside the lineage directory.\n- Output `FANOUT_LINEAGE_COMPLETE:gpt55-fast-1`.\n\n## Critical Context\n- Current dashboard state: iteration `2 of 10`, status `ITERATING`, `resolvedQuestions: 2`, `openQuestions: 3`, `convergenceScore: 0.40`.\n- Remaining key questions:\n  - system-spec-kit tooling borrow.\n  - reference migration across commands/agents/READMEs/advisor corpus.\n  - fallback-router real GLM-5.2 → MiMo-v2.5-Pro fallback wiring.\n- `resource-map.md` was absent at init; coverage gate skipped.\n- Ruled out:\n  - Flattening runtime and workflow packets into one directory.\n  - Moving directories first and relying on generated contracts to catch up.\n\n## Relevant Files\n- `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-1`: only writable artifact boundary.\n- `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-1/deep-research-state.jsonl`: append-only loop state.\n- `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-1/deep-research-strategy.md`: current plan and next focus.\n- `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-1/deep-research-findings-registry.json`: resolved/open questions and findings.\n- `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-1/deep-research-dashboard.md`: current progress dashboard.\n- `.opencode/commands/deep/assets/deep_research_auto.yaml`: workflow contract and path-coupling evidence.\n- `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/SKILL.md`: hub/backend ownership evidence.\n- `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/README.md`: runtime backend-only evidence.\n- `.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/shared/review-research-paths.cjs`: system-spec-kit artifact-root implementation borrowed by runtime.","time":{"start":1783487117894,"end":1783487138216},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_04594a9b02b4c948016a4dda8de5788191a852ee34bff7aa3e","phase":"final_answer"}}}}
