{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1783487161343,"sessionID":"ses_0bfeb66caffeOOxX7Bbz2N0h6m","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_Mbc1tFQRhpGAHAmQDTSAEYoS","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-1/deep-research-dashboard.md","offset":1,"limit":220},"output":"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-1/deep-research-dashboard.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Deep Research Dashboard - gpt55-fast-1\n2: \n3: ## 1. STATUS\n4: - Topic: Deep-loop unification merge-design stress test\n5: - Started: 2026-07-08T04:57:16Z\n6: - Status: ITERATING\n7: - Iteration: 2 of 10\n8: - Session ID: fanout-gpt55-fast-1-1783486518892-2qss01\n9: - Parent Session: none\n10: - Lifecycle Mode: new\n11: - Generation: 1\n12: \n13: ## 2. PROGRESS\n14: \n15: | # | Focus | Track | Ratio | Findings | Status |\n16: |---|-------|-------|-------|----------|--------|\n17: | 1 | Structural layout and ownership seams | architecture | 0.82 | 6 | complete |\n18: | 2 | Bidirectional path-coupling inventory | migration | 0.74 | 7 | complete |\n19: \n20: - iterationsCompleted: 2\n21: - keyFindings: 5\n22: - openQuestions: 3\n23: - resolvedQuestions: 2\n24: \n25: ## 3. QUESTIONS\n26: - Answered: 2/5\n27: - [x] Structural layout and ownership seams (iteration 1)\n28: - [x] Bidirectional path-coupling repair (iteration 2)\n29: - [ ] system-spec-kit tooling borrow\n30: - [ ] Reference migration across commands/agents/docs/advisor corpus\n31: - [ ] GLM-5.2 to MiMo fallback-router wiring\n32: \n33: ## 4. TREND\n34: - Last 3 ratios: 0.82 -> 0.74 (declining)\n35: - Stuck count: 0\n36: - Guard violations: none\n37: - convergenceScore: 0.40\n38: \n39: ## 5. DEAD ENDS\n40: - Flattening runtime and workflow packets into one directory: contradicts hub/backend contracts (iteration 1).\n41: - Move directories first and rely on generated contracts to catch up: generated contracts are outputs and source files carry old paths (iteration 2).\n42: \n43: ## 6. NEXT FOCUS\n44: System-spec-kit tooling borrow and external contract boundaries.\n45: \n46: ## 7. ACTIVE RISKS\n47: - User explicitly constrained this detached lineage to write only inside the lineage artifact directory; spec.md write-back and memory save are skipped.\n48: - Broad markdown inventories are noisy; use targeted exact-path searches next.\n49: - Do not treat compiled command contracts as authoritative source files; regenerate them after source-path rewrites.\n\n(End of file - total 49 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Deep Research Dashboard - gpt55-fast-1\n\n## 1. STATUS\n- Topic: Deep-loop unification merge-design stress test\n- Started: 2026-07-08T04:57:16Z\n- Status: ITERATING\n- Iteration: 2 of 10\n- Session ID: fanout-gpt55-fast-1-1783486518892-2qss01\n- Parent Session: none\n- Lifecycle Mode: new\n- Generation: 1\n\n## 2. PROGRESS\n\n| # | Focus | Track | Ratio | Findings | Status |\n|---|-------|-------|-------|----------|--------|\n| 1 | Structural layout and ownership seams | architecture | 0.82 | 6 | complete |\n| 2 | Bidirectional path-coupling inventory | migration | 0.74 | 7 | complete |\n\n- iterationsCompleted: 2","truncated":false,"loaded":[],"display":{"type":"file","path":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-1/deep-research-dashboard.md","text":"# Deep Research Dashboard - gpt55-fast-1\n\n## 1. STATUS\n- Topic: Deep-loop unification merge-design stress test\n- Started: 2026-07-08T04:57:16Z\n- Status: ITERATING\n- Iteration: 2 of 10\n- Session ID: fanout-gpt55-fast-1-1783486518892-2qss01\n- Parent Session: non