{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1783487202194,"sessionID":"ses_0bfeb66caffeOOxX7Bbz2N0h6m","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_2IITOUzvXaSaAOiAK97TtUiH","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/references/script_interface_contract.md","offset":35,"limit":12},"output":"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/references/script_interface_contract.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n35: ## 2. SHARED PROCESS CONTRACT\n36: \n37: ### Loader Contract\n38: \n39: - Scripts are Node executables with `#!/usr/bin/env node`.\n40: - Line 2 is `'use strict';`.\n41: - Scripts resolve `system-spec-kit/scripts/node_modules/tsx/dist/loader.mjs`.\n42: - If `DEEP_LOOP_TSX_LOADED !== '1'`, the script spawns Node with `--import <tsx-loader>` and original args.\n43: - The child receives cwd, env plus `DEEP_LOOP_TSX_LOADED=1`, and stdin when stdin is not a TTY.\n44: \n45: ### Stdout Contract\n46: \n\n(Showing lines 35-46 of 166. Use offset=47 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"## 2. SHARED PROCESS CONTRACT\n\n### Loader Contract\n\n- Scripts are Node executables with `#!/usr/bin/env node`.\n- Line 2 is `'use strict';`.\n- Scripts resolve `system-spec-kit/scripts/node_modules/tsx/dist/loader.mjs`.\n- If `DEEP_LOOP_TSX_LOADED !== '1'`, the script spawns Node with `--import <tsx-loader>` and original args.\n- The child receives cwd, env plus `DEEP_LOOP_TSX_LOADED=1`, and stdin when stdin is not a TTY.\n\n### Stdout Contract\n","truncated":true,"loaded":[],"display":{"type":"file","path":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/references/script_interface_contract.md","text":"## 2. SHARED PROCESS CONTRACT\n\n### Loader Contract\n\n- Scripts are Node executables with `#!/usr/bin/env node`.\n- Line 2 is `'use strict';`.\n- Scripts resolve `system-spec-kit/scripts/node_modules/tsx/dist/loader.mjs`.\n- If `DEEP_LOOP_TSX_LOADED !== '1'`, the script spawns Node with `--import <tsx-loader>` and original args.\n- The child receives cwd, env plus `DEEP_LOOP_TSX_LOADED=1`, and stdin when stdin is not a TTY.\n\n### Stdout Contract\n","lineStart":35,"lineEnd":46,"totalLines":166,"truncated":true}},"title":".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/references/script_interface_contract.md","time":{"start":1783487202191,"end":1783487202193}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_0f15a2db0dd5f9e0016a4ddae2054c819081505e5579d3da99"}},"id":"prt_f401f0389001qSRp4farskcyD5","sessionID":"ses_0bfeb66caffeOOxX7Bbz2N0h6m","messageID":"msg_f401ede8e001NMk64kEjG57Sry"}}
